# =============================================================================
# COMMENTS & NOTES
# =============================================================================
# This .gitignore is designed for a Next.js landing page project
# It follows GitHub best practices and includes comprehensive patterns
# while ensuring critical project files are not ignored
#
# Key principles:
# 1. Ignore dependencies (node_modules)
# 2. Ignore build outputs (.next, out, dist)
# 3. Ignore sensitive data (.env files, keys)
# 4. Ignore OS-specific files (.DS_Store, Thumbs.db)
# 5. Ignore temporary and cache files
# 6. Keep essential project files and assets
#
# If you need to ignore additional files, add them above with comments
# explaining why they should be ignored.
.vercel
